{"tid":2179886,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"【窮狗鳩噏】啱啱無聊睇咗基本嘅形家風水，好似幾實用，連羅盤方位都唔洗睇","createTime":"2020-08-29T12:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T03:09:29.000Z","uid":125976,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6838014afba890cdf9bcb82b8852e0fdf074b06a","tid":2179886,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"如果有人行梗衰運，留意吓你哋坐嘅辦公室 / 屋企長期活動睡眠地方：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 最好諗辦法令你嘅左邊高過右邊，同埋右邊 (白虎方) 忌動（即係唔好有人走嚟走去），𠵱個白虎方係最凶，犯咗會工作壓力大、易病、睡眠差同事倍功半<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 你嘅後面（玄武方）最好有靠山同高過前面 (凳背夠高都算)，後面忌動（𠵱個可能難啲，但如果有動可以搵嘅遮吓，覺察唔到為乾淨），犯咗易有小人事非暗傷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 房 / 客廳中間（騰蛇、勾陳方）忌放嘢（尤其係大嚿嘢），如果唔係影響工作集中力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之唔想黑氣纏身（我試過都真係幾應吓），你自己坐嘅右邊、後邊都要靜、高、乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n形家（即係肉眼睇得見嘅）風水嘅影響佔整體 6-7 成，反而理家（肉眼睇唔到嘅）方位只影響 3-4 成，所以應過嗰啲乜柒飛星五黃病位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7Xq3iK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7Xq3iK.jpg&h=979804fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98943c2c7df68f506c6789b798085b0f33e45397","tid":2179886,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"迷信柒頭<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"d8a9fdd206735153a0aaa2d957bb8b1484043fc6","tid":2179886,"uid":3091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"547045a1ead74a74b4c9708f618beb20c644ff97","tid":2179886,"uid":8785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n間房唔夠50呎可以點擺陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d14d0b1d5c2697dc8e6df0f636ae26a1ed390c","tid":2179886,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"547045a1ead74a74b4c9708f618beb20c644ff97","tid":2179886,"uid":8785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n間房唔夠50呎可以點擺陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"我咪話唔洗諗方位擺陣住囉，自己搞掂啲左青龍右白虎（左高又低）𠵱啲基本嘢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n形家唔搞掂，你計晒方位飛星放幾十隻蟾蜍都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020b7977770a65470bfee25bc6cd1840fcda2044","tid":2179886,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98943c2c7df68f506c6789b798085b0f33e45397","tid":2179886,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"迷信柒頭<br />\n<br />\n弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:51:13.000Z","msg":"連登仔仲會信星座 宗教 中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備好比人屌未?"},{"pid":"61310371b37f632d8d1413cd052e5a445d05da26","tid":2179886,"uid":134059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"2個個好似幾實用咁<br />\n<br />\n以office為例，當座位背後無靠山而且有人流動，感覺好似容易招惹是非，自己睇唔清環境之餘，同事會覺得你用背脊得住佢，講你是非自己都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}